{
  "texts": [
    "The o/p gate contains the neuron's o/p.",
    "Considering that the sequence of i/p is, the calculation formula for each LSTM neuron parameter at time t is as follows by Eqs.",
    "(20), (21), (22), (23) and (24).",
    "Where it, ft, otis the i/p of the i/p gate, forget gate, o/p gate at time t respectively, xt is i/p to the LSTM neuron t, ht-1 hidden layer's o/p state at t-1 respectively.",
    "In addition, Wi, W f, Wo is weight of the i/p gate, the forget gate, o/p gate of the neuron at time t, and bi, b f, booffset vectors, Wc weight between the i/p and the cell unit, ht o/p of the hidden layer at time t and S is the sigmoid function."
